Because you spend a lot of time preparing students for exams, administering and grading exams, Zeraki Analytics gives you a new and easy way to analyze and visualize exam results. From a mark sheet to a variety of graphs and pre-formatted tables, Zeraki Analytics makes it easy for teachers to focus on their work.
descriptionShort: We'll transform your academic data to help you find insights.
